{"tid":1561400,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"何超瓊聯合國發言：香港示威令數以百計小商戶結業","createTime":"2019-09-11T14:50:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T14:58:40.000Z","uid":66324,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"07e22a14200e01b327804822e639257aa7528985","tid":1561400,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:50:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1480066-20190911.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1480066-20190911.htm&d=y6uglPlKbSLkZz%2BcPL4okYICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=c4fee381\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1480066-20190911.htm&h=80f8a9c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1480066-20190911.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n香港各界婦女聯合協進會主席何超瓊，出席聯合國人權理事會會議並發言。她表示自六月九日開始，香港發生了大約130場示威，當中超過110次都演變成暴力及違法行為，令到數以百計的小商戶結業，很多人都失業。她又提到有學生受鼓勵而參加罷課，不同年齡層孩子在校園及網上被灌輸仇恨警察及反政府觀念，拒絕參與的人會受到惡意騷擾、恐嚇及欺凌，呼籲國際社會譴責這些組織者和「網紅」。<br />\n<br />\n另外，正在德國的香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒，回應傳媒提問時就表示，除非北京回應，香港人對政制改革的訴求，否則示威一定會持續。"},{"pid":"003f97f1bcfef8fb990c67b6efd13f2ddf6f5773","tid":1561400,"uid":5682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:51:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />915 遮打見！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F